@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.14
    v2 = wp.exp(0.50)
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.sin(v2 + 0.75) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.93)))
    v1 = wp.exp((0.13 / v0))
    v2 = 0.58
    v1 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.34 - tmp + 0.19)) / (v0 - (v1 + 0.08 + v1 + 0.44)))
    v1 = (v2 / wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.99)))
    v0 = (0.67 / wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.37)))
    data[tid] = v0
